          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Description of Services</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Tusdatos provides the following services:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Background Checks:</strong> Comprehensive background checks and verification services</li>
            <li><strong>Sanction list screening:</strong> Screening against international sanctions and PEP databases</li>
            <li><strong>Compliance Services:</strong> Implementation of Anti-Money Laundering and Counter-Terrorism Financing – AML/CTF (LAFT – Lavado de Activos y Financiación del Terrorismo) and PTEE (PTEE – Plan de Transparencia y Ética Empresarial) frameworks</li>
            <li><strong>Consultation:</strong> Expert guidance on regulatory compliance</li>
            <li><strong>Training:</strong> Staff training and documentation services</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">As a user of our services, you agree to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-6">
            <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
            <li>Obtain necessary consents for background checks</li>
            <li>Comply with applicable laws and regulations</li>
            <li>Use our services only for lawful purposes</li>
            <li>Maintain the confidentiality of your account</li>
            <li>Notify us of any unauthorized use of your account</li>
            <li>Pay all fees and charges in a timely manner</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Service Limitations and Disclaimers</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.1 Service Availability</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            We strive to provide reliable and continuous service, but we do not guarantee uninterrupted access. Our services may be temporarily unavailable due to maintenance, updates, or circumstances beyond our control.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.2 Data Accuracy</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            While we use reliable sources and verification methods, we cannot guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of all information provided through our services. Users should independently verify critical information.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.3 Compliance Results</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Our compliance services provide guidance and implementation support, but ultimate compliance responsibility remains with the client. We recommend consulting with legal counsel for specific legal advice.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Payment Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Payment terms and conditions:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-6">
            <li>Fees are due upon service delivery or as specified in your service agreement</li>
            <li>All fees are non-refundable unless otherwise specified</li>
            <li>Late payments may result in service suspension</li>
            <li>Prices are subject to change with 30 days' notice</li>
            <li>Additional fees may apply for rush orders or custom services</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            All content, trademarks, service marks, trade names, logos, and intellectual property rights in our services are owned by Tusdatos or our licensors. You may not use, reproduce, or distribute our intellectual property without written permission.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Your privacy is important to us. Our collection and use of personal information is governed by our Privacy Policy, which is incorporated into these Terms by reference. By using our services, you consent to our Privacy Policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Confidentiality</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Both parties agree to maintain the confidentiality of any proprietary or confidential information shared during the course of our business relationship. This obligation survives the termination of these Terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, Tusdatos shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including but not limited to loss of profits, data, or business opportunities.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Our total liability for any claims arising from these Terms or our services shall not exceed the amount paid by you for the specific service giving rise to the claim.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">10. Indemnification</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Tusdatos, its officers, directors, employees, and agents from and against any claims, damages, losses, or expenses arising from your use of our services or violation of these Terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">11. Termination</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">These Terms may be terminated:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-6">
            <li>By either party with written notice</li>
            <li>Immediately for material breach of these Terms</li>
            <li>Upon completion of the agreed-upon services</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Upon termination, your right to use our services ceases immediately, and you must destroy any copies of our materials in your possession.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">12. Governing Law and Dispute Resolution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Colombia. Any disputes arising from these Terms or our services shall be resolved through good faith negotiations, and if unsuccessful, through binding arbitration in Bogotá, Colombia.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">13. Force Majeure</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to circumstances beyond their reasonable control, including but not limited to acts of God, government actions, war, civil disturbance, or other events of force majeure.
